Additionally, the paper could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as few-shot learning is a common problem in computer vision tasks. Other possible sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as these sub-categories are also related to machine learning and could potentially involve few-shot learning tasks.
